      Name "IdsDrugClmFkey"
      Description "IDS Drug Claim  foreign keying."
      NextID "117"
      Container "V0"
      FullDescription =+=+=+=
 
COPYRIGHT 2004 BLUE CROSS/BLUE SHIELD OF KANSAS CITY 
COPYRIGHT 2005 BLUE CROSS/BLUE SHIELD OF KANSAS CITY 

DESCRIPTION:     Takes the sorted file and applies the foreign keys.    
      
PROCESSING: get foreign key as stated above and create file to load to DRUG_CLM, create a file for adjusted claims
                         NDC sk is determined in IdsDrugClmPkey, and just passed to this job
                         Pull Argus claims only with fill dt => FillDtMin for Claim Mart

MODIFICATIONS:
            BJ Luce        8/2004          -   Originally Programmed - phase 2.0
            Brent Leland 09/10/2004  -  Added Default rows for UNK and NA
                                                      -  Added link partitioner
            BJ Luce      09/24/2004   -   turn off logging for DAW, Legal Status and 3 tier
            BJ Luce      03/2005             change logging to X for DAW, legal status and 3 tier
                                                          name adjustment file to IdsDrugClmAdj.dat
            BJ Luce     03/29/2005        for reversals, change check for A08 for argus claims
            BJ Luce     08/2005             RX deductibles file format
             BJ Luce     08/01/2005        add recon date
            BJ Luce      08/31/2005        add output file for claim mart P_CLM_DM_EXTR.datDrug#RunID#
            BJ Luce      12//2005          add new input and output fields for Medicare Part D staff tracker 1736
            Brent Leland  04/18/2006   Changed table name P_DRUG_CLM to W_DRUG_CLM and change date field to char.
                                                         Hard coded file names
                                                         Changed parameters to environment values.
                                                         Removed Fill date parameter and logic.  Input no longer has old records that need to be excluded from the Claim Mart.
            Brent Leland 05/08/2006     Changed claim mart output column format and file name.


